				class="mt-6 text-3xl"
				iterations="1"
				duration="900"
				delayBetween="30"
				trigger="visibleonce"
				fullNode="false"
				retain="transform"
				easing="cubic-bezier(0.375, 0.8, 0.5, 0.375)"
				animations="transform: [scale(0), rotate(359deg), scale(0.5), rotate(42deg), scale(1)]"
			>
				Below you will find all attributes you can use to control the animations.
			</X>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="p-6">
